reviewText: 5 stars for the product. Love this original Zumba. 2 stars for the seller. It didn't look new.
This is an excellent full body workout with great music!
I loved the price and it was exactly what I had been searching for over a year.  It's the best Zumba dvd for live interaction and fun.
I really love doing this DVD I have lost 35lbs with doing this 4 days a  week and counting my calories and it has me sweating all the time I totally recommend this DVD

I think beto the guy who invented it keeps you motivated and engaged at times its like hes talking to you and giving you one on one advice:), of course you cant just do it once and expect results, keep doing it as much as you can and eat healthier.!!

The exercises are fun & relatively easy to follow with practice. The performers with the live audience keep me moving and motivated.
Try it, you'll like it!

Too physical for me.  I am at the 50+ group, and very out of shape.  This is a live group; a lot of hooping and hollering.  Quite annoying to me, because I am a very quiet type.  You'll need a lot of space, which I don't have, but good luck to you, if that is your thing.
not enough stars, you get a 10
